t/160864/', '', 'Acetohexamide, Guar gum, Pramlintide, Alogliptin, Rosuvastatin, Empagliflozin, Dulaglutide, Exenatide, Miglitol, Albiglutide, Rosiglitazone, More', '', 1767369485);
